    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> gnocchi</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water </strong>with a large pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the gnocchi for 3-4 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the gnocchi</p>",
